kclaude (0.3.7-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Cookie button: sends 🍪 into whichever session KClaude last launched
    or focused, via `tmux send-keys` (optional dependency — greys out
    without tmux installed). Raises the target window first.

 -- Agundur <info@agundur.de>  Wed, 15 Jul 2026 07:00:00 +0200

kclaude (0.3.6-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Session export: copy sessions.json to a timestamped backup.
  * Session import: scan ~/.claude/projects for sessions not yet saved,
    suggest a name from each session's latest title, add them one by one.
  * Live name-sync: a running session's /rename'd name is mirrored into
    KClaude's own session list, so the two displays don't drift apart.
  * launch() now passes --name so Claude Code's own prompt-box chip and
    /resume picker show the same name as KClaude.

 -- Agundur <info@agundur.de>  Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0200

kclaude (0.3.5-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Pin button to keep the panel popup open (panel only, not on a desktop
    instance where there's no popup to pin).
  * Click a session that's already running raises its window instead of
    spawning a duplicate (KWin scripting, unique window title per session).
  * A session's row flashes red when it starts waiting for input.
  * The OS notification popup is skipped when the panel is already open —
    the row flash covers it, avoids a redundant popup.

 -- Agundur <info@agundur.de>  Sat, 11 Jul 2026 08:30:00 +0200

kclaude (0.3.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed a rare plasmashell crash (Qt6 QML engine bug) caused by repeated
    insert/delete on a plain JS object used to track in-flight status/quota
    polls; switched to a Map instead.

